@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title Edit Record Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant EditCommand
participant RecordList
participant Record
participant Ui
participant Storage

User -> Resumake: edit INDEX [fields]
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: EditCommand
Resumake -> EditCommand: execute(list)
EditCommand -> RecordList: getRecord(index)
EditCommand -> Record: setTitle/setRole/setTech/setFrom/setTo
EditCommand -> Ui: show update status
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare + write if changed
@enduml
